import { FormWrapper } from "./FormWrapper"

export function AddressForm() {
    return (
        <FormWrapper title='Address Details'>
        <label>Street</label>
        <input autoFocus required type="text"/>
        <label>City</label>
        <input required type="text"/>
        <label>State</label>
        <input required type="text"/>
        <label>Zip</label>
        <input required type="text"/>
        </FormWrapper>
    )
}
